name: Chinese zodiac series#2 (tiger)
description: The Chinese zodiac tiger is one of the 12 zodiac signs in the Chinese calendar. This zodiac sign is symbolized by the tiger. People born with the zodiac sign of the tiger tend to be lucky in life. He has the talent of a leader, ambition to excel, and loves to work hard. In addition, he is wise in the world of business, romance, and war. He is also admired for his zeal, and ability, generosity and generosity.
